init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She looked around at the other people as they all watched life play out on the screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As the movie went on, Jane found herself not really watching.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She saw Jane looking at her, and smiled.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Oh, I've been here for a long time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Jane asked, more loudly than she meant to.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Why are you so interested in them?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The friend forgave him, and they both felt better.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She watched George's departure, and noticed that even the older woman looked relieved.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Something that was a part of her memory, but not.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Jane looked at her, and thought about it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Jane was surprised to realize that she felt excited and alive again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "How about we watch the movie together, and see what else we can learn?"
